    <thetext>The independently contributed Policy Editors (WTP-based and XEF) should be integrated to provide a single Editor to create, edit and assign WS-Policy documents to service objects in the context of the Service Creation project.

Subtasks:
1. Integration of WTP-based and XEF Policy Editors
   - Design GUI, common interfaces and extension points
   - Redesign module structure
   - Rework WTP based Policy Editor to support required functionality
      - collapse/expand
      - unlimited hierarchy of alternatives
      - property view
      - link to XEF Editor)
   - Implement XEF Editor interfaces, its invocation and events handling
   - QA of integrated solution
   - Documentation
2. Handling of XML Schemas to define custom WS-Policy assertions
3. Integrate Policy handling with other STP components
   - Service Creation project (JAX-WS)
   - Intermediate Model</thetext>
